metadata.name: 𝕷𝖆𝖘𝖙 𝖒𝖊𝖆𝖑
metadata.description:
Amid corruption, we sought control,
Dominion over all, our ultimate goal.
Devious talks, our ambition extreme,
But it was our final dream, or so it seemed.

Blind ambition, our toll it took,
Bold desires, our path it shook.
Our pride led us to a terrible fall,
Our scheme shattered, reality appalled.

In this world where power corrupts,
Our last meal a symbol of our ill-gotten lust.
The ultimate toll of our arrogant dream,
A heartbreaking song of our extreme reality's scheme.
